We are now bigger, better and larger than life! Call us a brand that amps up any space at any time.💯

We didn't stop at just adding premium products, we strived to transform our brand image, starting with premium packaging and of course our logo.✨

Besides, we are expanding as a brand. What started as a family of 10k is now 163k. With the love from our customers, we have stepped onto global shipping (selected countries) as well.🌍

We too evolved into a better team with our brand.🥰

Here's to growth and shift!💪🏻

We are saying goodbye to our dearest panda with a heavy heart! 🥹

But you know, some goodbyes are just not sad but bring in happiness and enthusiasm. 😇

We kept on adding more premium products to our line, that help you revamp any space anytime. Thus, we felt the need for a change. The change of our brand image which led to the transformation of our logo! ✅

With mixed feelings, we welcome this shift with all our hearts. 🙃
